fields.description:
When a distributed shell application starts running and a container launch fails the web service call to the API,
{noformat}
http://<RM web address>/ws/v1/timeline/DS_CONTAINER/<container_attempt_id>{noformat}
return a "Not Found". The message returned in this case should be improved to signify that a container launch failed.

